    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Chicago</placeName>
                <date>Sept. 10 1865</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser Esq.</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Sir</p>
            <p>I have two children going to school<lb/> they are in want of <add>חומשים</add>
                with<lb/> Engl. Translation. I see in your<lb/> Occident you have some in
                Duodecimo<lb/> for sale, also <add>תפילות</add> with <sic>englisch</sic><lb/>
                Translation, will you be so kind &amp;<lb/> send to <persName>Foreman Bro</persName>
                on <placeName>Third Street<lb/> near Market</placeName> 2 sets of <add>תפילה
                    חומשים</add><lb/> with the lowest cash prices, they<lb/> love to send many goods
                to <placeName>Chicago</placeName><lb/> &amp; will be so kind &amp; pack it with<lb/>
                I will <sic>remitt</sic> on <sic>reciept</sic> of them,<lb/>
                <sic>providet</sic>
                <sic>they</sic> children can use it in<lb/> school. <sic>send</sic> also Bill for
                    <persName>A. &amp; H.<lb/> Kohn</persName> for the Occident till <date>April
                    1866</date><lb/> I remain yours Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">H. I. Kohn</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
